title: frank7301
author: frank7301
content: this came up when logging in.Ubus error: Command failed: Permission deniedIs my password/login wrong?

comments.author: BitMaxz
comments.body: Yes possible if the error only came up after you type your login and password credentials.If you forgot the right login password you can reflash the unit through SD card flashing and setup the unit again.Or reset it by following this method below and other methods to reset your unit to factory default.- https://docs.braiins.com/os/20.04/open-source-en/Setup/2_advanced.html#sd-factory-reset
